    `bim-ai <command> [args]

Commands:
  bootstrap                           GET /api/bootstrap (projects + models)
  init-model --project-id <uuid> [--slug slug] [--template <id>]
                                       POST empty model row (agents use BIM_AI_MODEL_ID from output)
